snippet.title: Nanos Just Cause 3 Multiplayer - Beta Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
More information about the first Beta release: https://community.nanos.io/index.php?/topic/360-jc3mp-beta-release-announcement/

"nanos JC3:MP" is a multiplayer modification for Just Cause 3 allowing playing on customisable dedicated servers. Be sure to visit our homepage at http://just-cause.mp/

Video Creators

Phantom: https://www.youtube.com/phantomproductionsfr
Mp3Charlie: http://youtube.com/mp3charlie
__________________________
Songs

"Shake It Up!"
Written By Guillaume Amphoux
Performed By Gyom
Courtesy Of Method House/Position Music
